<TEXT>
   The jury found Younis guilty on three counts in the six-count
indictment, and acquitted him on the remaining three.
   Younis faces life imprisonment for the most serious charge,
taking hostages.
   The verdict was viewed as an affirmation of a 1984 law asserting
